50|$|Mr Clarke {{worked as}} a hod carrier and brick cutter for Frank Staddon Ltd from 2 April to 23 June 2001. He was on holiday until 24 July 2001, {{and went back to}} work but was not paid between 23 June and 24 July. His {{contract}} said <b>holiday</b> <b>pay</b> is included within the daily rate of £85 per day (an August pay slip said: ‘Basic 8.689 Holiday 0.756 = £85 per day’), but in his contract before August 2001 there was no breakdown of the <b>holiday</b> <b>pay</b> in his pay slips. He claimed <b>holiday</b> <b>pay</b> from 2 April to 16 November 2001.|$|E
